# Magic Code Words for Cursor

Use these “magic code words” in Cursor as shorthand prompts to your LLM-driven workflows. Simply say **Iris, `codeword`** (or `uv codeword` in CLI) and the system will expand to the full natural-language instruction.

| Code Word                                                                                                           | Funny Alias                                                                                                                                                                                                          | LLM Prompt                                                                                     | Recommended Implementation                                                                                          |                                                                                                                                        |               |                                                                                         |                                 |
| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------- |
| **allup**                                                                                                           | **IrisExpress**                                                                                                                                                                                                      | "Stage all changes in the repo, commit with a descriptive message, and push to the Git remote."    | **LLM prompt only**                                                                                                 |                                                                                                                                        |               |                                                                                         |                                 |
| **redgreen**                                                                                                        | **traffic jam**                                                                                                                                                                                                      | "Run the complete test suite and report any failures or successes."                            | **Use:** `uv run pytest` (or `uv run npm test`)                                                                     |                                                                                                                                        |               |                                                                                         |                                 |
| **pristine**                                                                                                        | **sparkle**                                                                                                                                                                                                  | "Auto-format and lint the entire codebase according to project style guidelines."              | **Use:** `uv run black . && uv run ruff .`                                                                          |                                                                                                                                        |               |                                                                                         |                                 |
| **buildit**                                                                                                         | **Chrona HQ**                                                                                                                                                                                                        | "Build all project artifacts, including binaries, bundles, and Docker images as configured."   | **Use:** `uv build`                                                                                                 |                                                                                                                                        |               |                                                                                         |                                 |
| **launchpad**                                                                                                       | **Nova Launch**                                                                                                                                                                                                      | "Start the full local development environment (Docker Compose, servers, databases)."           | **LLM prompt only**                                                                                                 |                                                                                                                                        |               |                                                                                         |                                 |
| **scribe**                                                                                                          | **IrisQuill**                                                                                                                                                                                                        | "Generate or update project documentation from code, comments, and docstrings."                  | **LLM prompt only**                                                                                                 |                                                                                                                                        |               |                                                                                         |                                 |
| **branchme**                                                                                                        | **LilySplit**                                                                                                                                                                                                        | "Prompt for a new feature branch name, create it, switch to it, and set its upstream."         | **LLM prompt only**                                                                                                 |                                                                                                                                        |               |                                                                                         |                                 |
| **snapit**                                                                                                          | **TimeCapsule**                                                                                                                                                                                                      | "Create a snapshot commit of all staged changes with a timestamped message."                   | **LLM prompt only**                                                                                                 |                                                                                                                                        |               |                                                                                         |                                 |
| **dockit**                                                                                                          | **ArborDock**                                                                                                                                                                                                        | "Build the Docker image if needed and run the main service container."                         | **LLM prompt only**                                                                                                 |                                                                                                                                        |               |                                                                                         |                                 |
