| **blastoff**                                                                                                        | **VioletFlight**                                                                                                                                                                                                     | "Deploy the current build to the staging or production environment and summarize the outcome." | **LLM prompt only**                                                                                                 |                                                                                                                                        |               |                                                                                         |                                 |
**statusquo**                                                                                                       | **GitGossip**                                                                                                                                                                                                        | "Show an enhanced Git status: branch info, ahead/behind counts, stash list, and file summary." | **Use:** `uv run git status --verbose` (no built-in `uv statusquo`)                                                 |                                                                                                                                        |               |                                                                                         |                                 |
| **todozap**                                                                                                         | **UVTasker**                                                                                                                                                                                                         | "Update completed tasks in TODOS.md, then open it for editing."                              | **LLM prompt only**                                                                                                 |                                                                                                                                        |               |                                                                                         |                                 |

